<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٤ص١٥٩:</span> <span class="c3">{مَكْظُومٌ}</span> <span class="c2">(٢)</span>: كَظِيمٌ، وَهُوَ مَغْمُومٌ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
